### CONTACTS - LOCAL
### =========================

### Get all contacts
GET http://localhost:8080/contacts


### Create a new contact (POST) - MUST return { "id": "..." }
POST http://localhost:8080/contacts
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "Samuel",
  "lastName": "Exposito Ruiz",
  "email": "samuel@example.com",
  "favoriteColor": "Blue",
  "birthday": "1995-01-01"
}

### ðŸ”´ IMPORTANT:
### After running the POST above, copy the returned "id" and paste it below:
@id = PASTE_NEW_ID_HERE


### Get a single contact by id (GET)
GET http://localhost:8080/contacts/{{id}}


### Update a contact by id (PUT) - should return 204
PUT http://localhost:8080/contacts/{{id}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "Samuel",
  "lastName": "Exposito Ruiz",
  "email": "samuel.updated@example.com",
  "favoriteColor": "Black",
  "birthday": "1995-01-01"
}


### Delete a contact by id (DELETE) - should return 204
DELETE http://localhost:8080/contacts/{{id}}


### Confirm deletion (should be 404)
GET http://localhost:8080/contacts/{{id}}


